_sText:
Gg_quadrate is a map with a dark gloomy theme to it.  Lighting is fairly dim but still possible to see where you\'re going and what you\'re doing.  There are some darker spots than others (maybe camp in the dark places?)


Textures are a little different that what people are used to, but I\'m always trying something new.

There are 40 player slots, FPS rate is pretty good.

.bsp and .nav are included in the .zip file.




This would be my second map published to the public :)

Happy gaming everybody!
